room_title: Escape room "Spell Breaker" by Great Escape of Central Texas in Killeen
room_address: 4400 E. Central Texas Expy Killeen, TX 76543
room_description: As filmmaking students, you are always intrigued by legends of ghosts, goblins and of course, witches. One such legend drives your team to hike the Black Hills, a densely thick forest region hidden away near Burkittsville.  It is said that the most powerful witch lives in seclusion in these hills and as legend would have it, anyone who seeks to find her lair only finds themselves cursed, never to return.  Well, it is only a legend, or is it?
